snippet.title: Longvinter Early Access Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
Early Access begins February 24, 2022

Fish, farm, craft, gather, cook, loot or steal from other players, and build a campsite or a village with your friends in an open-world multiplayer sandbox game without rules!

Longvinter is made by Uuvana Studios.

https://store.steampowered.com/app/1635450/Longvinter/

https://longvinter.com/

https://discord.gg/zdKvKrSsVq

https://twitter.com/uuvanastudios

https://www.instagram.com/teouuvana/
